Things are going haywire in Bungoma county but the MCAs are quietly going about their business, doing nothing about it, Kanduyi MP Wafula Wamunyinyi (pictured) has complained. ... our MCAs have no ability to check the performance of the executive, affecting the quality of services delivered to the people, he said.Wamunyinyi spoke in Bungoma town on Saturday. He said the MCAs do not pressure the executive to improve services.